Gabriel Barylli https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gabriel_Barylli 0 Gabriel Barylli (born 31 May 1957) is an Austrian actor and film director. He has appeared in more than 40 films and television shows since 1981. He won the Silver St. George award for Best Actor for his role in A French Woman at the 19th Moscow International Film Festival.
